feed.title: FEX-Emu
feed.subtitle: A fast linux usermode x86 and x86-64 emulator

entry.title: Hello world
entry.content:
FEX-Emu is a linux usermode x86 and x86-64 emulator for arm64. It aims to bring x86 and x86-64 games to arm64 laptops.

It can already run full fledged applications like GIMP or clang and games such as FTL and UT2004.

For more information, please visit our project page on github
entry.summary: FEX-Emu is a linux usermode x86 and x86-64 emulator for arm64. It aims to bring x86 and x86-64 games to arm64 laptops.
